</div>

<div class="about-data">
<strong>About This Data:</strong> Content based on federal bankruptcy law (Title 11, U.S. Code §§ 362, 541, 542), <em>In re Mwangi</em>, 432 B.R. 812 (9th Cir. BAP 2010), and related automatic-stay case law. Bank policies cited are based on public litigation records and published attorney commentary; individual bank policies change and may differ from what is described here. This is educational content, not legal advice.
</div>

